M||tx|---
M||titl|Prevent Hydration Mismatch w/o Flickering
M||impa|md
M||impa|avoids visual flicker and hydration er
M||tags|rendering, ssr, hydration, localStorage, flicker
M||tx|---
M|Prev|tx|When rendering cn that depends on client-side storage (localStorage, cookies), avoid both SSR breakage and post-hydration flickering by injecting a synchronous script that updates the DOM before rc hydrates.
M|Prev|**In|**
M|Prev|tx|```tsx
M|Prev|func|{ children: ReactNode }) {
M|Prev|tx|// localStorage is not available on server - throws er
M|Prev|tx|const theme = localStorage.getItem('theme') \|\| 'light'
M|Prev|tx|return (
M|Prev|tx|<div className={theme}>
M|Prev|tx|{children}
M|Prev|tx|</div>
M|Prev|tx|)
M|Prev|tx|}
M|Prev|tx|```
M|Prev|tx|Server-side rendering will fail bc `localStorage` is undefined.
M|Prev|**In|**
M|Prev|tx|```tsx
M|Prev|func|{ children: ReactNode }) {
M|Prev|tx|const [theme, setTheme] = useState('light')
M|Prev|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Prev|tx|// Runs after hydration - causes visible flash
M|Prev|tx|const stored = localStorage.getItem('theme')
M|Prev|tx|if (stored) {
M|Prev|tx|setTheme(stored)
M|Prev|tx|}
M|Prev|tx|}, [])
M|Prev|tx|return (
M|Prev|tx|<div className={theme}>
M|Prev|tx|{children}
M|Prev|tx|</div>
M|Prev|tx|)
M|Prev|tx|}
M|Prev|tx|```
M|Prev|tx|cp first renders w/ default value (`light`), then updates after hydration, causing a visible flash of incorrect cn.
M|Prev|**Co|**
M|Prev|tx|```tsx
M|Prev|func|{ children: ReactNode }) {
M|Prev|tx|return (
M|Prev|tx|<>
M|Prev|tx|<div id="theme-wrapper">
M|Prev|tx|{children}
M|Prev|tx|</div>
M|Prev|tx|<script
M|Prev|tx|dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{
M|Prev|__ht|`
M|Prev|tx|(fn() {
M|Prev|tx|try {
M|Prev|tx|var theme = localStorage.getItem('theme') \|\| 'light';
M|Prev|tx|var el = document.getElementById('theme-wrapper');
M|Prev|tx|if (el) el.className = theme;
M|Prev|tx|} catch (e) {}
M|Prev|tx|})();
M|Prev|tx|`,
M|Prev|tx|}}
M|Prev|tx|/>
M|Prev|tx|</>
M|Prev|tx|)
M|Prev|tx|}
M|Prev|tx|```
M|Prev|tx|The inline script executes synchronously before showing the element, ensuring the DOM already has the correct value. No flickering, no hydration mismatch.
M|Prev|tx|This pattern is esp useful for theme toggles, us preferences, authentication states, and any client-only data that shd render immediately w/o flashing default values.